data.title: 1958 Dutch Grand Prix
data.meta_description: Find all the stats for the 1958 Dutch Grand Prix, including race, qualifying & practice results, standings, lap time comparisons, and race reports.
data.text:
The 1958 Dutch Grand Prix started May 26, 1958 on Circuit Park Zandvoort in Zandvoort, Netherlands. Stuart Lewis-Evans started from pole position with Stirling Moss next to him. Tony Brooks started from third place.

In 2 hour, 04 minutes and 49 seconds Stirling Moss finished the race in first place.The podium was completed with Harry Schell in second and Jean Behra in third place.

After the 1958 Dutch Grand Prix, Stirling Moss is first in the Formula 1 World Championship with 17 points. Moss is 5 points ahead of Luigi Musso.
